# Tooltip

**Figma:** [Tooltip](https://www.figma.com/design/AW4jk9SLPKlSqYt6NZ1QK5/Qure-%3C%3E-Figma-Design-system?node-id=280-23459&p=f&m=dev)

Structure, placements, styling, and behavior below are derived from Figma node 280:23459.

---

## Variables (from design-system-tokens.mdc)

| Use | Token |
|-----|-------|
| Container | `--bg-base-default` or `--bg-base-tertiary` |
| Border | `--border-base-default` |
| Title | `--text-base-default` |
| Body | `--text-base-secondary` |

---

## Structure

| Element | Style |
|---------|-------|
| Title | Bold; larger font size; `--text-base-default` |
| Body text | Regular weight; smaller font size; `--text-base-secondary` |
| Pointer/arrow | Triangular; extends from center of edge; points toward trigger |

---

## Placements

| Placement | Tooltip position | Pointer |
|-----------|------------------|---------|
| Top | Below trigger | Extends upward from top edge |
| Bottom | Above trigger | Extends downward from bottom edge |
| Left | Right of trigger | Extends leftward from left edge |
| Right | Left of trigger | Extends rightward from right edge |

Auto-flip on viewport edge.

---

## Styling

| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| Container | `--bg-base-default` or `--bg-base-tertiary` |
| Border | Optional `--border-base-default` |
| Shadow | Shadow sm or md |
| Padding | Space/200–300 |
| Max width | max-w-xs |

---

## Behavior

- **Trigger:** Hover, focus, or focus-visible.
- **Show:** After ~300ms delay.
- **Hide:** On mouse leave.
- **Rule:** Never block interactive elements.

---

## Implementation guidelines

- Use tokens from `design-system-tokens.mdc` only.
- A11y: `role="tooltip"`; `aria-describedby` on trigger; keyboard-dismissable.
- Do not invent variants; implement only what exists in Figma node 280:23459.
